pathfinder
Class Pathfinder

java.lang.Object
  pathfinder.Pathfinder

public class Pathfinder
extends Object

Implementation of A* path finding algorithm for maps where coordinates are represented by jawa.awt.Point The implementation details and heuristic functions were taken from http://theory.stanford.edu/~amitp/GameProgramming/Heuristics.html

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Egor Tsinko

Method Detail

setScale

public void setScale(double scale)
Sets new scale for results of the heuristics. This parameter is neccessary if average cost of travel between two points is not 1. The result of the heuristic function is multiplied by the scale.
The default value is 1.0

Parameters:
scale - new scale

setHeuristic

public void setHeuristic(IHeuristic heuristic)
Sets the heuristic function. The default is DiagonalNotEqual

Parameters:
heuristic -
